  (text "HUB75 DRIVER NOTES (IPC-2221B):\\nU2 SN74HCT245: R1 G1 B1 R2 G2 B2 CLK LAT (3.3V→5V)\\nU3 SN74HCT245: ADDR_A-E OE (3.3V→5V). A6-A8 NC.\\nVCC of both 74HCT245 = +5V_EXT_HUB75 (NOT +3V3)\\n  74HCT inputs: VIH min=2.0V — 3.3V logic drives reliably\\n  74HCT outputs swing to VCC (5V) — required for HUB75\\nDIR pin 1 = GND via 0Ω resistor (A→B fixed direction)\\n~OE pin 19 = GND via 0Ω resistor (always enabled, no GPIO)\\nBypass caps C8/C9: 100nF within 2mm of VCC pin 20 on each IC\\nGND pins on J1 (4 8 14 16): via directly to GND plane L2\\nNo via in signal path between U2/U3 outputs and J1"
    (at 20 145 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "c5ed434d-d48a-47d0-bae1-ce660a677001")
  )
